OL,3,CThousands back grieving family's call
OL,4,Cfor tougher conditions for drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FThe family of a father who was killed
OL,8,Fby a drunk driver say tougher legal
OL,9,Frules could have prevented the tragedy
OL,10,Fwhich took his life.
OL,12,FTim Burgess, from Frodsham, Cheshire,
OL,13,Fdied six months ago after his vehicle
OL,14,Fwas struck head-on by a car driven by
OL,15,Fa man who was on bail after another
OL,16,Fcrash only ten days earlier.
OL,18,FMore than 100,000 people have now
OL,19,Fsigned a petition in Tim's memory
OL,20,Fdemanding bail restrictions on those
OL,21,Faccused of dangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
