OL,4,Cfor tougher conditions for drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FChester Crown Court heard Eldred, from
OL,8,FNorthwich, was late for work and was
OL,9,Fseen by witnesses to be driving
OL,10,Ferratically ` stalling at traffic
OL,11,Flights, driving on the wrong side of
OL,12,Fthe road, and failing to maintain a
OL,13,Fsteady speed.
OL,15,FHe later pleaded guilty to causing
OL,16,Fserious injury and death by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving and was sentenced in October
OL,18,F2024 to 12 years in prison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
