OL,3,CThousands back grieving family's call
OL,4,Cfor tougher conditions for drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FTim's family learned that Eldred had
OL,8,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fdangerous driving 10 days before the
OL,10,Fcrash in which killed their loved one.
OL,12,FDealing with the earlier incident
OL,13,FCrewe magistrates were told Eldred had
OL,14,F100 milligrams of alcohol in 100
OL,15,Fmillilitres of his blood, exceeding
OL,16,Fthe limit of 80.
OL,18,FHe was also found to be unfit to drive
OL,19,Fthrough drugs when he was involved in
OL,20,Fthe collision, after which he fled the
OL,21,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
