OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FEldred pleaded guilty to three charges
OL,8,Fand was handed a further eight weeks'
OL,9,Fimprisonment, to be served
OL,10,Fconcurrently to his 12 year term.
OL,12,FNow Tim's sister Linzi Stewart, 49,
OL,13,Fhas launched the petition, calling on
OL,14,Fthe government to amend the law so
OL,15,Fthose charged with dangerous driving
OL,16,Fwould have their licences immediately
OL,17,Frevoked, pending trial and sentencing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
