OL,3,CThousands back grieving family's call
OL,4,Cfor tougher conditions for drink
OL,5,Cdrivers
OL,7,FThe petition also calls for repeat
OL,8,Fdangerous driving offenders to be
OL,9,Fremanded in custody or closely
OL,10,Fmonitored if released.
OL,12,FLinzi said: "If he had been remanded
OL,13,Fin custody or had some bail conditions
OL,14,Fput on him or his license revoked, Tim
OL,15,Fwould possibly still be alive.
OL,17,F"We need to see some law changes
OL,18,Fregarding this because too many people
OL,19,Fare being killed on the roads by
OL,20,Fdangerous drivers who are allowed to
OL,21,Freoffend."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
